data.description:
Affordable single level living, plus a second bedroom upstairs! This 2 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath home for sale is located in the heart of Peculiar, MO, just about 2 blocks from Peculiar Elementary, in the Raymore-Peculiar School District. A large open living room, eat-in kitchen, and walk in pantry are just a few of the amenities that this home has to offer. With almost 1,500 square feet of finished living space, PLUS storage in the utility room and outdoor shed, this house has a lot of space to offer in the 2-bedroom market. There is new paint and carpet in many areas of the house, and a front patio enclosure that is perfect for drinking your morning coffee. The fully fenced back yard has lots of room for the pets to run around, and a fire pit is there to welcome you on a chilly Friday evening in the fall.
This home is located just south of the downtown Peculiar area, and it is only a 2-minute walk to Peculiar’s Mckernan Park. With grocery stores, gas stations, and restaurants available in town, you don’t have to venture too far from home to enjoy a night out, but if you do want to venture a little further away, downtown Kansas City is about a 30-minute drive. 
Cass Regional Medical Center is located just 6.3 miles south and Research Belton Hospital is 8.2 miles north. 
2022 Taxes were $1,117.02.
